parts.text: I will generate a 3D rendering of a whimsical scene. Imagine a pink pig with small, delicate white wings soaring through the air. It's wearing a dapper black top hat perched jauntily on its head. Below, a sprawling futuristic city unfolds with sleek, silver buildings interconnected by glowing blue pathways. Lush green plants and trees sprout from various rooftops and balconies, creating a vibrant contrast with the metallic architecture. The sky above is a soft, hazy blue.
